---
// Acciones rápidas
---
<section aria-labelledby="quick-actions-heading">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2 id="quick-actions-heading" class="section-title">¿Cómo puedes ayudar hoy?</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Cada acción acerca a una mascota a su familia</p>
  </div>
  <div class="actions-grid">

    <div class="action-card">
      <div class="action-icon" style="background: var(--rojo-bg)">
        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--rojo)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/>
          <line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/>
          <line x1="11" y1="8" x2="11" y2="11"/>
          <line x1="11" y1="14" x2="11.01" y2="14"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="action-body">
        <h3 class="action-title">Perdí mi mascota</h3>
        <p class="action-desc">Reporta para que la comunidad te ayude a encontrarla</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/reportar" class="action-btn" style="background: var(--rojo)">Reportar ahora</a>
    </div>

    <div class="action-card">
      <div class="action-icon" style="background: var(--verde-bg)">
        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--verde)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="action-body">
        <h3 class="action-title">Encontré una mascota</h3>
        <p class="action-desc">Ayuda a reunirla con quien la está buscando</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/reportar" class="action-btn" style="background: var(--verde)">Reportar ahora</a>
    </div>

    <div class="action-card">
      <div class="action-icon" style="background: var(--azul-bg)">
        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--azul)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="action-body">
        <h3 class="action-title">Soy veterinario</h3>
        <p class="action-desc">Ofrezco atención gratuita a mascotas afectadas</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/veterinarios" class="action-btn" style="background: var(--azul)">Registrarme</a>
    </div>

    <div class="action-card">
      <div class="action-icon" style="background: var(--naranja-bg)">
        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accion)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="action-body">
        <h3 class="action-title">Quiero donar</h3>
        <p class="action-desc">Insumos, alimentos, medicinas o recursos para los centros</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/insumos" class="action-btn" style="background: var(--accion)">Ver necesidades</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.section-header { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
.section-title {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--texto);
  margin: 0;
}
.section-sub {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: var(--texto-sec);
  margin: 4px 0 0;
}
.actions-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .actions-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }
}
.action-card {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 1rem;
  padding: 1.25rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  transition: box-shadow .2s;
}
.action-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }
.action-icon {
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.action-body { flex: 1; }
.action-title {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--texto);
  line-height: 1.3;
  margin: 0 0 4px;
}
@media (min-width: 768px) { .action-title { font-size: 1rem; } }
.action-desc {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--texto-sec);
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin: 0;
}
.action-btn {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 10px 16px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: filter .15s;
  min-height: 44px;
  line-height: 24px;
}
.action-btn:hover { filter: brightness(0.9); }
</style>
